        </p>
        <p class="license-terms">
          My goal with this license is that people can't use this as part of
          commercial projects (unless otherwise negotiated, I will probably say
          yes if you ask), and that any improvements anyone makes are upstreamed
          to the official version so everyone can benefit.
        </p>
        <p class="license-terms">
          <b>Important:</b>As the sentences are from Tatoeba and Open Subtitles,
          you must also comply with their licenses if you redistribute the
          sentences. I honestly don't really understand the legality of this
